			<div class="post-3940 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-data-mining category-electronic-data category-training tag-bitcoin tag-credit-card tag-database tag-edward-snowden tag-personal-information tag-privacy-disclosures tag-vpn post_box top" id="post-3940">
